====Select a page====
[[File:Abroad - 1882.djvu|thumb|right|150px|page=13|This is page 13]]
Images can be excerpted from [[DjVu]] or [[Portable Document Format|Pdf]] files, with an optional ''page'' parameter.

<code><nowiki>[[File:Abroad - 1882.djvu|</nowiki>'''<span style="color:red;">page=''number''</span>'''<nowiki>|alt=Example alt text]]</nowiki></code>

