Scale the file to be no wider and no higher than the specified number of pixels (e.g. <code>100x150px</code>).

<code><nowiki>[[File:Example.png|</nowiki>'''<span style="color:red;">''Width''x''Height''px</span>'''<nowiki>|alt=Example alt text]]</nowiki></code>

