===Links===
Ordinarily, a file will include a hyperlink to its [[Help:File page|description page]], a page with information about the file itself. The options below allow the link to point to a different page or to be disabled. For images, the link is the image itself. Videos include an information icon below the video.

Unless the file is public domain attribution must be provided in some other fashion. See [[Wikipedia:Images linking to articles]] for more information.

====Modify file link====
[[File:Example.png|150px|right|link=Wikipedia|alt=Example alt text]]
The image acts as a hypertext link to the specified page. Do not enclose the page name in square brackets. If '''''Page''''' is a URL, the image acts as an external link; otherwise it links to the named Wikipedia page. [[#Image maps|Image maps]] offer more possibilities.

<code><nowiki>[[File:Example.png|</nowiki>'''<span style="color:red;">link=''Name of page''</span>'''<nowiki>|alt=Example alt text]]</nowiki></code>

